        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">From here, you are free to talk to your AI for as long as you so desire. Be it on political debates, questions about life, or its opinions on pineapple on pizza, everything goes. Just don't be illegal, which is hopefully not too much to ask.</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
